<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Donate — Vihaan's Vision</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css?v=20260716" />
  <script src="/page-views.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Vihaan's Vision home">
    <span class="logo-mark">☀️</span>
    <span class="logo-copy">
      <strong>Vihaan's Vision</strong>
      <small>A world where every child smiles</small>
    </span>
  </a>
  <nav>
    <a href="/">Home</a><a href="/events/">Events</a><a href="/donate/" style="color:#2f6f9f">Donate</a><a href="/donation-events/">Donation Events</a><a href="/testimonials/">Testimonials</a><a href="/team/">Team</a><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
  </nav>
</header>


<main>
  <section class="page-hero donate-hero">
    <h1 class="page-title">Help turn filament into smiles.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Donations support materials and supplies used to create 3D-printed keychains, toys,
      and future gifts for children. AI class donations also help fund this mission.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn light" href="/donation-events/">View Donation Events</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="donation-support-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">What Donations Support</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🧵</div>
        <h3>3D Printing Materials</h3>
        <p>Filament, colors, replacement parts, and supplies needed to make the gifts.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">📦</div>
        <h3>Packaging</h3>
        <p>Gift bags, cards, labels, and safe packaging so every item feels special.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="callout">
      <h2>Every donation becomes something a child can hold.</h2>
      <p>
        A small contribution can help create keychains, toys, bookmarks, and future creative gifts.
        The goal is not just to make objects — it is to create a moment of joy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Double Your Impact with Employer Matching</h2>
    <div class="story-box">
      <p>
        Many companies match charitable donations, allowing your gift to have twice the impact
        at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        Vihaan’s Vision is fiscally sponsored by Hack Club, a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit.
        After making your donation:
      </p>
      <ol class="numbered-list">
        <li>Check whether your employer offers donation matching.</li>
        <li>Submit your donation through your company’s matching portal.</li>
        <li>Use the donation receipt you receive after donating.</li>
        <li>If approved, your employer’s matching gift will be directed to support Vihaan’s Vision through our fiscal sponsor.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="story-box tax-box">
      <p>
        Vihaan’s Vision is fiscally sponsored by Hack Club, a registered 501(c)(3)
        nonprofit organization (EIN 81-2908499). Donations are tax-deductible to the
        extent allowed by law. After donating, you’ll receive an official tax receipt by email.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="final-donation-action">
      <a class="btn primary" href="https://hcb.hackclub.com/donations/start/vihaan-s-vision" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Make a Donation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <p>☀️ A world where every child smiles — one gift, one child, one ray at a time.</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
